# FRC App Component Rules

## frc-app/modern-component-design: Modern Component Design Standard

This rule defines the modern, compact, and visually consistent design pattern for FRC app components.

### **üé® Color Palette & Usage**
- **Primary Orange** (`#f57c00`): Labels, titles, headers, counts, floating labels
- **Success Green** (`#43a047`): Success actions, positive elements, selected item borders  
- **Danger Red** (`#f44336`): Delete/remove actions, error states
- **Card Background** (`#333333`): Main content cards, highlighted list items
- **Input Background** (`#252525`): Input fields, secondary elements, list headers
- **Text Colors**: White for main content, `#999` for secondary/meta information
- **Border Colors**: `#444` for subtle separations between list items

### **üÉè Card Design Pattern**
All information cards should follow this structure:
```html
<ion-card style="background: #333333; border-radius: 8px; margin: 4px 0; border-left: 4px solid [THEME_COLOR];">
  <ion-card-content style="padding: 12px;">
    <!-- Content with proper typography hierarchy -->
  </ion-card-content>
</ion-card>
```
- **Border-left colors**: Orange `#f57c00` for primary/static info, Green `#43a047` for selected/active items
- **Compact spacing**: 4px margins, 8px border radius, 12px internal padding

### **üìù Input Fields Standard**
All input fields should use this consistent pattern:
```html
<ion-item style="--background: #252525; --border-radius: 8px; --padding-start: 12px; margin: 4px 0; --min-height: 44px; align-items: center;">
  <ion-label position="floating" style="color: #f57c00;">Label Text</ion-label>
  <ion-input style="color: white;" [formControl]="control"></ion-input>
  <ion-button fill="solid" slot="end" style="--background: #43a047; --border-radius: 6px; --height: 32px; --padding-start: 8px; --padding-end: 8px; margin: 0 4px;">
    <ion-icon name="icon-name" slot="icon-only" style="font-size: 0.9rem;"></ion-icon>
  </ion-button>
</ion-item>
```

